    "description": "<p><span>At the start of your turn during a conflict, if you are driving your <strong>personal vehicle</strong>, you may spend 10 Mind Points<strong>. </strong>If you do, choose one option:</span></p><ul><li><p><span>The next time you deal damage during this turn, deal <strong>【SL × 2】</strong> extra damage.</span></p></li><li><p><span>The next time you suffer damage before the start of your next turn, that damage is reduced by <strong>【SL × 2】</strong> (applied before damage Affinities).</span></p></li><li><p><span>You recover from a status effect of your choice among <strong>slow</strong> and <strong>weak</strong>.</span></p></li></ul><hr /><p><strong>You Receive:</strong> @EFFECT[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.XoMumkEXtYQOF7Et]{Effect: Heart in the Engine (Offensive)} or @EFFECT[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.VM5F00GYKYInRjgM]{Effect: Heart in the Engine (Defensive)}</p>",
